  h2 Tables
  p When using tables remember about appropriate content grouping with <code>thead</code> and <code>tbody</code>. 

  .table-responsive
    table
      thead
        tr
          th #
          th Name
          th Surname
          th Email
      tbody
        tr
          td 1
          td Adam
          td Brault
          td 
            a adam@andyet.net
        tr
          td 2
          td Henrik 
          td Joreteg
          td 
            a henrik@andyet.net
        tr
          td 3
          td Adam
          td Baldwin
          td
            a baldwin@andyet.net

