  h3 Outlined tables
  p Use <code>table-outlined</code> class for additional border around the <code>table</code>. For hover effects on rows add <code>table-with-hover</code>.

  .table-responsive
    table.table-outlined.table-with-hover
      thead
        tr
          th #
          th Name
          th Surname
          th Email
      tbody
        tr
          td 1
          td Adam
          td Brault
          td 
            a adam@andyet.net
        tr
          td 2
          td Henrik 
          td Joreteg
          td 
            a henrik@andyet.net
        tr
          td 3
          td Adam
          td Baldwin
          td
            a baldwin@andyet.net

