  h3 Table with error states
  p To add validation states to table rows use <code>table-cell-success</code>, <code>table-cell-alert</code> and <code>table-cell-error</code> respectively.

  .table-responsive
    table
      thead
        tr
          th #
          th Name
          th Surname
          th Email
      tbody
        tr.table-cell-success
          td 1
          td Adam
          td Brault
          td 
            a adam@andyet.net
        tr.table-cell-alert
          td 2
          td Henrik 
          td Joreteg
          td 
            a henrik@andyet.net
        tr.table-cell-error
          td 3
          td Adam
          td Baldwin
          td
            a baldwin@andyet.net
        tr
          td 4
          td Amy
          td Lynn Taylor
          td
            a amy@andyet.net